{"tid":2229760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟11月峰會可能商討對華政策","createTime":"2020-10-04T15:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T15:29:38.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84af0eea06a431581e7facbfdb041958659886bf","tid":2229760,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/jiangjingling/jjl-03042019120918.html/jjl304.jpg/@@images/b93ec169-94fd-47e2-9abc-5ca573624e03.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fpinglun%2Fjiangjingling%2Fjjl-03042019120918.html%2Fjjl304.jpg%2F%40%40images%2Fb93ec169-94fd-47e2-9abc-5ca573624e03.jpeg&h=adbc4d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設於比利時布魯塞爾的歐盟總部（Public Domain）<br />\n<br />\n歐盟國家和政府領導人計劃在11月16日再次舉行峰會，商討對華政策。這是10月2日，正在布魯塞爾舉行的歐盟峰會公佈的會議日期。<br />\n<br />\n據德國之聲報導，歐盟希望在年底前就投資與中國達成協議，由此改善歐洲公司進入中國市場的機會。這將成為自由貿易談判的先決條件。<br />\n<br />\n但歐盟與中國的關係受到中國人權和領土政策的影響。中國在香港和新疆問題上的政策，以及對台灣採取的強硬立場，引來歐盟領導人的明確反對。<br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾本週三（9月30日）對外表示，歐盟在與中國打交道時，要明確表達在人權等話題上的態度。她譴責了中國對少數民族的殘暴政策，並表達了對中國香港政策的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n（責編：王允）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/2-10032020105726.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2F2-10032020105726.html&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=67506f41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/2-10032020105726.html</a>"},{"pid":"d7751f7208965f1430769f1f4b1e087f27abca31","tid":2229760,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"下年11月?"},{"pid":"483b460038e16d425d687a2bd4eb435bf93560a9","tid":2229760,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">簽聯署</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n德國政府官方聯署：夠數德國就必須喺國會討論制裁中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6adfbfce79f8d0872380f0e21ba5dffe21e1aaa2","tid":2229760,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7751f7208965f1430769f1f4b1e087f27abca31","tid":2229760,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"下年11月?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"今年"}]}